[[CS Sfaxien]] and [[WA Tlemcen]] advanced to the finals.

==Group stage==

The eight teams were drawn into two groups of four. Each group was played on one leg basis. The winners and runners-up of each group advanced to the [[#Knock-out stage|semi-finals]].

